        For Couples · Launching October 2026
      </div>

      <h1 class="hero__title">
        <span class="hero__title-top">Making something <span class="hero__title-italic">good</span></span>
        <span class="hero__title-bottom"><span class="hero__title-italic hero__title-italic--lg">even better.</span></span>
      </h1>

      <div class="hero__visual">
        <div class="hero__visual-frame">
          <img src="/images/hero.png" alt="The Happy Class: a matte black lacquered box on dark walnut, lid lifted, warm golden light pouring out from inside." />
        </div>
        <div class="hero__visual-tag" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="hero__visual-tag-label">N°01</span>
          <span class="hero__visual-tag-name">Couples Edition</span>
