      <h2>Most couples don't need therapy.<br />They need <span class="accent">better structure.</span></h2>
      <p class="lead mx-auto">You're not in crisis. You're not falling apart. You love each other. But somewhere along the way, the conversations got shorter, the check-ins stopped, and "we're fine" became the answer to everything. You're good. But you know you could be better.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ WHAT IT IS ═══ -->
