    <div class="container">
      <div class="split">
        <div class="split__content">
          <p class="overline">What is The Happy Class</p>
          <h2>A kit you do together.</h2>
          <p>The Happy Class is a physical product. A beautifully designed box that gives you and your partner the structure to have the conversations you've been putting off. Not heavy therapy conversations. Real ones. Honest ones. The kind that remind you why you chose each other.</p>
          <p>It's guided. It's structured. It's actually fun. And when you're done, you know each other better than you did when you started.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="split__visual">
          <div class="product-frame">
            <img src="/images/product-kit.png" alt="The Happy Class kit: a matte black lacquered box, open, revealing premium dusty-rose and slate-blue cards and a brass pen." />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ WHO IT'S FOR ═══ -->
