          <div class="card__media">
            <img src="/images/vignette-couch.png" alt="A closed black lacquered box on a side table beside a leather chair, low warm light." />
          </div>
          <h3>You're solid</h3>
          <p>You're not in trouble. You're not looking for a lifeline. You just know that good relationships don't maintain themselves. They need attention.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__media">
            <img src="/images/vignette-coffee.png" alt="Two espresso cups across a dark walnut table, two cards between them, one dusty rose, one slate blue." />
          </div>
          <h3>You want to talk</h3>
          <p>Not about logistics. Not about the kids' schedule. You want the real stuff, the stuff that gets buried under busy. You just need a way in.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__media">
            <img src="/images/vignette-walk.png" alt="A man's hands holding the closed black box at chest height, charcoal cashmere sweater." />
          </div>
          <h3>Therapy feels like too much</h3>
          <p>You don't need a therapist. You don't need a crisis. You just need a framework that makes it easy to check in, on your own terms, in your own home.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ THE MECHANIC (pink + blue) ═══ -->
  <section class="section bg-charcoal">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">
        <p class="overline">Inside the box</p>
        <h2>Two papers. <span class="accent">One conversation.</span></h2>
        <p class="lead mx-auto" style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">There are things only your partner can see in you. There are things only you know about yourself. The kit is the third party in the room, the one that holds the structure so the two of you don't have to.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="papers">
        <figure class="paper paper--rose">
          <img src="/images/paper-pink.png" alt="A deep dusty-rose card on charcoal linen with a small gold-foil corner mark." />
          <figcaption>For what only you can see in them.</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="paper paper--storm">
          <img src="/images/paper-blue.png" alt="A muted slate storm-blue card on charcoal linen with a small gold-foil corner mark." />
          <figcaption>For what only you know about you.</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">
        <p class="tiny-note">Think of it as an annual relationship check-in. A physical for your partnership.</p>
      </div>
