    <div class="container">
      <div class="split split--reverse">
        <div class="split__visual">
          <div class="product-frame">
            <img src="/images/social-proof.png" alt="A man's hand holding a slate-blue card beside the black lacquered box and a black ceramic coffee mug." />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="split__content">
          <p class="overline">Validated</p>
          <h2>We tested it. <span class="accent">Men loved it.</span></h2>
          <p>We put The Happy Class in front of men, the audience most likely to resist anything that sounds like therapy. The response blew us away. They loved the name. They loved the concept. They didn't feel like they were being asked to "fix" something. They felt invited to do something good for their relationship.</p>
