      <h2>Couples first.<br />Then <span class="accent">everyone.</span></h2>
      <p class="lead mx-auto" style="margin: 1.5rem auto var(--space-lg);">The Happy Class for Couples is just the beginning. The same framework works for every relationship that matters.</p>

      <div class="roadmap">
        <div class="roadmap__item roadmap__item--active">
          <span class="roadmap__dot"></span>
          <h4>Couples</h4>
          <p>October 2026</p>
        </div>
        <div class="roadmap__item">
          <span class="roadmap__dot"></span>
          <h4>Friends</h4>
          <p>2027</p>
        </div>
        <div class="roadmap__item">
          <span class="roadmap__dot"></span>
          <h4>Siblings</h4>
          <p>2027</p>
        </div>
        <div class="roadmap__item">
          <span class="roadmap__dot"></span>
          <h4>Mothers &amp; Daughters</h4>
          <p>2027</p>
        </div>
        <div class="roadmap__item">
          <span class="roadmap__dot"></span>
          <h4>Fathers &amp; Sons</h4>
          <p>2027</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ WAITLIST (final CTA) ═══ -->
  <section class="section bg-charcoal" id="waitlist">
    <div class="container container--narrow text-center">
      <p class="overline">Be the first</p>
      <h2>Save your spot.</h2>
      <p class="lead mx-auto" style="margin: 1.25rem auto 2.5rem;">The Happy Class for Couples launches October 2026. Drop your email and we'll let you know the moment it's ready.</p>

      <form class="waitlist-form" id="waitlist-form-bottom" data-waitlist>
        <div class="waitlist-form__row">
          <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="First name" class="waitlist-input" autocomplete="given-name" />
          <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email" class="waitlist-input" required autocomplete="email" />
        </div>
        <input type="text" name="company" autocomplete="off" tabindex="-1" class="waitlist-honey" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div class="cf-turnstile" data-sitekey="0x4AAAAAADAiulObYttIgvz0" data-theme="dark" data-size="flexible"></div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn--gold btn--large waitlist-submit">
          <span class="submit-text">Join the Waitlist</span>
          <span class="submit-loading" style="display:none;">Adding you…</span>
        </button>
        <div class="waitlist-status" role="alert"></div>
      </form>

      <p class="waitlist-fineprint">No spam. One email when it's ready. That's it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ FOOTER ═══ -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <p class="footer__brand">The Happy Class</p>
      <p class="footer__tagline">Making something good <span class="accent">even better.</span></p>
      <div class="footer__links">
        <a href="https://sandraweise.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">sandraweise.com</a>
        <span class="footer__sep">·</span>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/sandraweise/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a>
        <span class="footer__sep">·</span>
        <a href="https://sandraweise.com/podcast" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">A Better Question</a>
      </div>
